<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.7">
<l>cēyōṅkutaṇ tirumāliruñ cōlaimalai yuṟaiyum</l>
<l>māyāyeṉak kuraiyāyitu maṟaināṉkiṉu ḷāyō</l>
<l>tīyōmpukai maṟaiyōrcciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tāyōvuṉa taṭiyārmaṉat tāyōvaṟi yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Māyaṉ who dwells on cool Tirumāliruñcōlai hill with bamboo shooting up,</l>
<l>Tell me this! Whether you are in the four Vedas, you are on a watery bed</l>
<l>In Ciṟupuliyūr with Vedic experts whose hands tend the [temple] fire,</l>
<l>Or in your devotees’ hearts, I do not know.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
